name: Examples of Multiple Escape Characters

sections.text:
;; The following examples assume the readtable case of *readtable*
      ;; and *print-case* are both :upcase.
      (eq 'abc 'ABC) =>  true
      (eq 'abc '|ABC|) =>  true
      (eq 'abc 'a|B|c) =>  true
      (eq 'abc '|abc|) =>  false
